OL,3,CTrump risks looking like a loser over
OL,4,CHormuz - here are his options
OL,6,FPresident Trump is in a bind. Let's
OL,7,Fcall it the straitjacket of Hormuz.
OL,9,FThe received wisdom has been that he
OL,10,Fcan call a halt to the third Gulf War
OL,11,Fat any time he likes ` Just use the
OL,12,Fimmense damage inflicted on Iran's
OL,13,Fmilitary capabilities and nuclear
OL,14,Fprogramme as a metric for victory and
OL,15,Fwalk away.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
