OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774102277
OL,3,CTrump risks looking like a loser over
OL,4,CHormuz - here are his options
OL,6,FBut Iran's blockade of the Strait of
OL,7,FHormuz robs that narrative of
OL,8,Fcredibility. It's a global consequence
OL,9,Fthat highlights the limits of American
OL,10,Fpower. If he quits with the strait
OL,11,Fstill closed he risks looking like a
OL,12,Floser.
OL,14,FSince one man in a dinghy with an RPG
OL,15,Fcould put a hole in a tanker going
OL,16,Fthrough the strait, it's doubtful
OL,17,Fthere's a military answer to the
OL,18,Fproblem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
