OL,3,CTrump risks looking like a loser over
OL,4,CHormuz - here are his options
OL,6,FTrump hopes to have given himself some
OL,7,Fleverage over the Iranians by
OL,8,Fthreatening to capture Kharg Island,
OL,9,Fthe export terminal for 90% of Iran's
OL,10,Foil.
OL,12,FPlonked in the middle of the Gulf, the
OL,13,Fisland is vulnerable and Trump has
OL,14,Fpaved the way by destroying the
OL,15,Fmilitary defences on the island. So
OL,16,Ffar he has left the oil infrastructure
OL,17,Falone, but he has threatened it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
