OL,3,CTrump risks looking like a loser over
OL,4,CHormuz - here are his options
OL,6,FYesterday the world got a taste of
OL,7,Fwhat tit-for-tat strikes on the Gulf's
OL,8,Fmost important energy installations
OL,9,Fmean for the global economy.
OL,11,FIsrael attacked one of Iran's most
OL,12,Fvital plants and Iran retaliated by
OL,13,Fattacking one of Qatar's.
OL,15,FTrump maintains that the Israelis did
OL,16,Fnot make the Americans aware of their
OL,17,Fplan beforehand. Israeli officials say
OL,18,Fcategorically that notice was given.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
