OL,3,CTrump risks looking like a loser over
OL,4,CHormuz - here are his options
OL,6,FSince the whole episode is a re-run of
OL,7,Fwhat happened on March 8, when Trump
OL,8,Frebuked the Israelis for attacking oil
OL,9,Fdepots in Tehran and creating an
OL,10,Fapocalyptic vista, it seems highly
OL,11,Funlikely that Israel would not have
OL,12,Fnotified the Americans about their
OL,13,Fintentions to hit the big gas
OL,14,Finstallation yesterday.
OL,16,FSo why is the US President denying
OL,17,Fknowing anything about it?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
