OL,3,CTrump risks looking like a loser over
OL,4,CHormuz - here are his options
OL,6,FFirstly, he doesn't want to anger his
OL,7,Fgreat allies, the Qataris. The Trump
OL,8,Ffamily, as well as Messrs Witkoff and
OL,9,FKushner, have done big business deals
OL,10,Fwith Doha.
OL,12,FHow disgruntled might the Qataris feel
OL,13,Fif they thought he had given the nod
OL,14,Fto an Israeli strike that precipitated
OL,15,Fa retaliatory strike on their greatest
OL,16,Fasset?
OL,18,FMight they decide not to gift him the
OL,19,Fnew Boeing 747 he's planning to use as
OL,20,Fa replacement for Air Force One?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
