PN,31807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1774102277
OL,3,CTrump risks looking like a loser over
OL,4,CHormuz - here are his options
OL,6,FSecondly, might he want to impress
OL,7,Fupon the Iranians that he is willing
OL,8,Fto de-escalate things.
OL,10,FDenying any knowledge of the Israeli
OL,11,Fstrike allowed him to be seen to
OL,12,Fdemand from Benjamin Netanyahu a
OL,13,Fcommitment not to do it again.
OL,15,FBy portraying himself blissfully
OL,16,Fignorant of an incendiary move Trump
OL,17,Fmay just have left himself a way out,
OL,18,Fa trade even. You leave the Strait of
OL,19,FHormuz alone and we'll leave Kharg
OL,20,FIsland alone?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
